Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:29.93,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Vermelha(紅) 在12年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1000,655)}Vermelha(紅) 的現場直播
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}您現在看到的是押送Michiko Malandro被告的護送車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}前科累累 對相關场所屢次進行襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}雖然被告本人對此予以否認 但是被告的其它罪行不斷曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}今天將被收監於Diamandra監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}提起Diamandra 那是關押那些改過自新無望的重刑犯的陸上孤島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}她想重獲自由 恐怕只有等到死后了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}值得信賴的新晉升的少尉 Atsuko Jackson巡查
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}就這次的成果而言 她的努力是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(380,270)\fs48}無視規矩的焦糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,403號 有人探監
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很精神嘛 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我升職做巡查部長了 了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是你啊 Jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jumbo？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你逃掉的 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次脫獄已經是第3次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在一步步地前進哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對甩了你的男人 那么戀戀不舍么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發春的騷貨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko 你丫小時被我扁的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴上說不要 卻用陶醉的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會扁你的 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么！你這個婊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰被誰甩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko 你丫...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫給我等著！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ina Teles、Vinicio yazik、Elena Yugi、Jucelino Bielo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}爆炸發生在圣胡安(San Juan)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}以上播報的是在巴士爆炸事件中已經確認身份的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}雖然與本事件的關系尚不明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}非法組織的成員Hiroshi Morenos的死亡也被確認
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才電視上說了什么？ 說了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三月17日 扁豆鎮(lentilha)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}扁豆鎮(lentilha)發生搶劫案件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}自稱是Michiko Malandro的女人挾持顧客做人質 閉門不出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在已經對峙了大約快1個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}犯人有可能是監獄編號為403的犯人 現在確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是特別班 正在趕往現場 大約30分鐘后抵達現場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂叫個屁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天不見發福了嘛 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回Diamandra監獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么是Diamandra監獄？ 我不是Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 肥豬 你聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是讓我空歡喜一場的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怨就怨自己報過Michiko這個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Belenbauza Yamada
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛的 這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(200,200)}三月17日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(200,200)}距離橘子鎮(Laranja) 352km
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個剛才聽過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你到底想問什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么... 難道不很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道你有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息 休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的老爸很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro神父嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你提了個好問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說說看 Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi... Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽名字就是個帥哥 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥 又溫柔 我一下子就中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我這樣的女人啊 一下子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他走了 連告別都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算去見Hiroshi 現在他在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道點什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 你不是說他死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 巴士爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去見他是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么見？ 你是指去死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 把別人的話聽到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后？ 但是事情已經完了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi因為爆炸事件死掉已經是11年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幾歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9歲 下個月就10歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11減9
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了？ 你說我搞錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫當我是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把裙子掀起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吧？ 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽話！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想給別人看自己的肚臍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸是那么地可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是在問你 沒有油到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一滴都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你開個屁加油站啊 一滴總是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我問你 就憑一滴你的摩托能開嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直向前走 有個不大的鎮子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫竊賊鎮(Ladrao)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那里的市場去的話 價格雖然會貴些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會有的 汽油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直向前？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步行的話 3個小時左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喝嗎？ Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 請不要叫我Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Hana吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛才我就在看 你付錢了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么吧 這點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔在看著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓶子碎渣 誰去收拾？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我去收拾的話 你就給我看肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎摩托的女人來了 那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算伏擊她 離開了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果打錯算盤 那個家伙從窗戶沖了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從客廳用獵槍向她射擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4發？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐是警察嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官很大嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛從竊賊鎮(Ladrao)附近的加油站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人舉報稱 有疑似是Michiko Malandro的女子出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶著一名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全隊出動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}竊賊鎮(ladrao)的集市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛讓我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就像這樣凝視著我 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他的手就伸到我的胸脯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的耳朵經常清潔啊 真的很像他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的鼻子怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像啊 說起來你的下巴看上去也有點讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是相當讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些“零件”是從哪里(繼承)來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 你還是搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒... 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被這個孩子給拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日復一日 看著這照片上孩子的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管過多少年 我都不會認錯人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如你搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我身上沒有紋身的話 你要怎么辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我 也沒有閑到會帶著別人的孩子到處亂跑的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}關于今晨的綁架事件 出現了意想不到的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}闖入橘子鎮(Laranja)郊外圣佩德羅教堂的居住區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}綁架9歲的Belenbauza Yamada家的次女Hana的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在逃跑中的兇殘嫌疑犯被正式認定為越獄犯Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}犯罪的目標是教會和孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這個事件對于市民社會來說 這是不可饒恕的挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}當局正在盡全力繼續搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}雖然犯罪動機尚不明確 這次的事件被認為是以贖金為目的綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什么我都會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發過誓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 有嗎（紋身）？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 剛才有個帶小孩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 剛剛走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕 是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾啊 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快嘛 Jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又變大了吧 Jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許叫我Jumbo！ 你這個婊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婊子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫從小到現在什么都沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子里的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 你也配說別人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情叫“眼屎笑鼻屎(五十步笑百步)”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼屎？正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個鼻屎女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臟東西積累的太多 變得黑乎乎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 Atsuko 這樣太不成體統了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人！ 現在立刻放開小孩 自首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在什么地方遇到過你嗎 好像見過你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養育費怎么辦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我被欠債給逼死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很疼愛你的嗎 Hana！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你 你不相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個毒蛇婦! 母豬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主是不會袖手旁觀的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Michiko～ 一邊走～ 一邊拉褲子～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這么無聊地結束了 多沒勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你件好事 側耳過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是你想知道的男人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓路！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有和你玩玩了 我很爽 Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保險金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana在這里死掉的話 就有保險金進賬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怨恨我 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 你丫在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眼淚還是鼻涕啊 黏糊糊的好惡心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音都哽咽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin算是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎 Hatchin這個名字 很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko... 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指紋身的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過我相信你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是因為什么被關進監獄的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都沒做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點任而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點... 嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你的朋友唱的那首歌是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰... 在還是小鬼的時候總有過失敗吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你剛才直呼了我的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}待續
